  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Transition period: letter to the professional and business services sector
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Letter from the Secretary of State for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, Alok Sharma, to the professional and business services sector about actions they need to take from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

